INSERT INTO design_image_generations VALUES(1,'dc3a1aee-a38b-44d2-9a48-fb2106916196',2,replace('**1. Color Scheme:**\n\nBedroom: \n- Primary colors: Warm Oak (#BD9E70) and Neutral White (#F6F6F6). \n- Accent colors: Black (#000000), Metallic Copper (#6D4E46), and Dusty Rose (#DCA5A4).\n\nBathroom:\n- Primary colors: White (#FFFFFF) and Misty Grey (#AFB1B4).\n- Accent colors: Black (#000000) and Metallic Silver (#C0C0C0).\n\n**2. Layout Suggestions:**\n\nBedroom:\n- Place a king-size bed against the main wall. \n- Install floating shelves on either side of the bed for nightstands.\n- Position a comfortable armchair and floor lamp in a corner for a reading nook.\n- Leave ample space for a walk-in closet and vanity area.\n\nBathroom:\n- Arrange a free-standing bathtub under a window if possible.\n- Position the sink and vanity opposite the bathtub.\n- Allocate a separate area for the shower and toilet for privacy.\n\n**3. Material Recommendations:**\n\nBedroom:\n- Flooring: Parquet flooring in Warm Oak.\n- Walls: Neutral white paint with one accent wall in Warm Oak.\n\nBathroom:\n- Flooring: Slip-resistant porcelain tiles in Misty Grey.\n- Walls: White ceramic tiles with silver accents.\n\n**4. Furniture List:**\n\nBedroom:\n- King-size bed: 8,000 AED\n- Floating shelves: 1,000 AED\n- Armchair: 3,000 AED\n- Floor lamp: 1,500 AED\n- Vanity set: 5,000 AED\n\nBathroom:\n- Free-standing bathtub: 12,000 AED\n- Sink and vanity: 6,000 AED\n- Shower set: 4,000 AED\n- Toilet: 3,000 AED\n\n**5. Lighting Plan:**\n\nBedroom:\n- Install recessed lighting in the ceiling for overall illumination.\n- Use bedside lamps for task lighting.\n- Add a pendant light over the vanity for accent lighting.\n\nBathroom:\n- Use vanity lights for task lighting.\n- Install recessed lighting in the shower area.\n- Add a chandelier over the bathtub for a touch of luxury.\n\n**6. Decor Elements:**\n\nBedroom:\n- Use metallic copper accents for the hardware.\n- Hang a large mirror over the vanity.\n- Add a large area rug in Dusty Rose.\n\nBathroom:\n- Use metallic silver accents for the hardware.\n- Hang a framed piece of minimalist art.\n- Add fluffy white towels and bath mats.\n\n**7. Shopping List:**\n\nAll items can be sourced locally from stores like Marina Home, Crate and Barrel, and IKEA. \n\n**8. Timeline:**\n\nExpect the project to take 2-3 months to complete - 1 month for planning and ordering materials, and 1-2 months for the actual renovation. Remember to allow extra time for any unforeseen delays. \n\nThis plan respects the local climate by using materials that are suitable for Dubai''s hot and humid conditions. The color scheme and style are also in line with the classic, industrial aesthetic popular in the UAE. The budget has been respected, with the total coming in under the 100,000 AED limit.','\n',char(10)),'iaosfioajsf','["bedroom","bathroom"]','["classic","industrial"]',2,'completed','[{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-HsaVci1Zc8i7JhZzDBIlKyLh.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A31%3A16Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A31%3A16Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=b1a0ae1f-618f-4548-84fd-8b16cacd5485&sktid=a48cca56-e6da-484e-a814-9c849652bcb3&skt=2025-08-20T08%3A24%3A22Z&ske=2025-08-21T08%3A24%3A22Z&sks=b&skv=2024-08-04&sig=cKhjXDAmuJJIg75RsSPmLGrF%2BH5W\/89k1axVErG2ozA%3D","prompt":"Wide angle view, A beautiful classic and industrial bedroom, bathroom interior design in Dubai, UAE. High-quality architectural visualization with natural daylight. Clean, elegant space with attention to detail. Photorealistic rendering, interior design photography style. Luxurious finishes suitable for Dubai market. ","index":1},{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-0239RtPbcEkHREOdNcZatXPs.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A31%3A34Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A31%3A34Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=ed3ea2f9-5e38-44be-9a1b-7c1e65e4d54f&sktid=a48cca56-e6da-484e-a814-9c849652bcb3&skt=2025-08-20T16%3A31%3A34Z&ske=2025-08-21T16%3A31%3A34Z&sks=b&skv=2024-08-04&sig=\/TcbZ4lWvVCwHQtf2QqRRzaD5QRSJscV%2Bgdgf3beh4s%3D","prompt":"Close-up detail shot, A beautiful classic and industrial bedroom, bathroom interior design in Dubai, UAE. High-quality architectural visualization with warm evening lighting. Clean, elegant space with attention to detail. Photorealistic rendering, interior design photography style. Luxurious finishes suitable for Dubai market. ","index":2}]',NULL,'2025-08-20 16:30:41','2025-08-20 16:31:35','2025-08-20 15:48:43','2025-08-20 16:31:35');
INSERT INTO design_image_generations VALUES(2,'ddd0971f-840e-461a-9108-2d99850e5cca',2,replace('**1. Color Scheme**\n\nFor a classic industrial look, let''s mix neutral colors with bold accents. Here''s the specific color palette:\n\n- Base Colors: Benjamin Moore''s "White Dove" (OC-17) for the walls, a warm and soft white that is comforting.\n- Accent Colors: Sherwin William''s "Iron Ore" (SW 7069) for doors, window frames, and trim, a dark gray with a hint of warmth.\n- Secondary Accent: Use tones of copper and rustic brown for accessories.\n\n**2. Layout Suggestions**\n\nBedroom:\n- Place a king-sized bed against the main wall, with bedside tables on either side.\n- Opposite the bed, install a large industrial-style open shelf unit or metal-and-wood bookcase.\n- Allocate a corner for a relaxing reading nook with a comfortable armchair and a floor lamp.\n\nBathroom:\n- Install a standalone bathtub under a large window, if available, for natural light.\n- Opposite the tub, place a vanity unit with double sinks.\n- Enclose the shower area with black-framed glass.\n\n**3. Material Recommendations**\n\nFlooring:\n- Bedroom: Reclaimed wood flooring for a rustic industrial feel.\n- Bathroom: Cement tiles for an industrial look, with underfloor heating for comfort.\n\nWall Finishes:\n- Bedroom: White painted walls with one accent wall using exposed brick wallpaper.\n- Bathroom: White subway tiles for the shower area and half of the walls, with the upper half painted in white.\n\n**4. Furniture List**\n\n- King-sized Bed: Try the "Safina Wing Back Double Ottoman Bed" from Furniture 123. Estimated cost: 5,000 AED.\n- Bedside Tables: "Hemnes" from IKEA. Estimated cost: 600 AED each.\n- Open Shelf Unit: "Fjällbo" from IKEA. Estimated cost: 600 AED.\n- Armchair: "Strandmon" in dark gray from IKEA. Estimated cost: 1,200 AED.\n- Vanity Unit: Try the "Godmorgon/Odensvik" from IKEA. Estimated cost: 2,400 AED.\n- Standalone Bathtub: Try the "Freestanding Bathtub BW-01-L" from Badeloft. Estimated cost: 12,000 AED.\n\n**5. Lighting Plan**\n\n- Bedroom: Install pendant lights with a rustic finish on each side of the bed. Add a large chandelier with an industrial design in the center of the room.\n- Bathroom: Black industrial wall sconces next to the vanity mirror, and recessed ceiling lights for general illumination.\n- Use warm white (3000K) LED bulbs for a cozy atmosphere.\n\n**6. Decor Elements**\n\n- Bedroom: Industrial-style wall art, metallic accents, and a large area rug.\n- Bathroom: Copper bathroom accessories, a large round mirror with a black frame, and a tall indoor plant.\n- Both rooms: Use linen curtains in a neutral color for a soft, textural element.\n\n**7. Shopping List**\n\n- IKEA: Bed, bedside tables, shelf unit, armchair, vanity unit, curtains.\n- ACE Hardware: Paint, wallpaper, tiles, lighting fixtures, bathroom accessories.\n- United Furniture: Area rug, wall art, metallic accents.\n- Plantshop.ae: Indoor plants.\n- Badeloft: Freestanding bathtub.\n\n**8. Timeline**\n\nThis project can be completed within 6-8 weeks. Here''s a suggested timeline:\n\n- Weeks 1-2: Purchase and deliver materials.\n- Weeks 3-4: Paint and install wallpaper, lay the flooring.\n- Weeks 5-6: Assemble and install furniture, install lighting fixtures.\n- Week 7: Add decor elements.\n- Week 8: Final touches and clean-up. \n\nThis plan considers the local climate (e.g. underfloor heating for the cool winter months), local suppliers, and cultural preferences for privacy and luxury. It also combines the classic and industrial styles in a fresh and unique way.','\n',char(10)),'iaosfioajsf','["bedroom","bathroom"]','["classic","industrial"]',2,'completed','[{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-O6TfACbJEOVTnLkiqJuBUlVr.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A32%3A09Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A32%3A09Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=77e5a8ec-6bd1-4477-8afc-1