INSERT INTO design_image_generations VALUES(3,'a9042eb6-e5da-4127-937a-4f0fd01f4265',2,replace('**1. Color Scheme:**\nConsidering the modern-industrial style, the primary color palette would comprise neutral tones, such as greys and whites, accented with metallic colors like copper or steel.\n\n- Primary Wall Color: Dulux''s "Dusted Moss 2" [#C9BDAD]\n- Secondary/Accent Wall Color: Dulux''s "Night Jewels 3" [#4D4C4F]\n- Furniture and Accents: Copper, Steel, and Black\n\n**2. Layout Suggestions:**\nFor the bedroom, a queen-sized bed should be placed against the main wall with two bedside tables on either side. A dresser or seating area should be opposite the bed, depending on the available space. The dining room should have a large industrial-style table in the center, with seating for 6-8 people.\n\n**3. Material Recommendations:**\n- Flooring: Polished concrete or grey porcelain tiles for a modern, industrial feel.\n- Walls: Painted in the chosen color scheme. One accent wall in either room could feature exposed brick wallpaper for an industrial touch.\n- Ceiling: Simple plaster with recessed lighting. A high ceiling with exposed beams would complement the industrial style if possible.\n\n**4. Furniture List:**\n- Bedroom: Queen-sized bed (2500 AED), two bedside tables (1000 AED each), wardrobe (3000 AED), seating area or dresser (2000 AED)\n- Dining Room: Industrial-style dining table (3000 AED), 6-8 chairs (500 AED each), sideboard for storage (2500 AED)\n\n**5. Lighting Plan:**\nUse a mix of overhead, ambient, task, and accent lighting. Industrial-style metal pendant lights are perfect for the dining area, while wall sconces or table lamps would work well in the bedroom. Recessed lighting can be used for general ambient lighting.\n\n**6. Decor Elements:**\nHang large, abstract artworks on the walls. Use copper or steel accents wherever possible, such as in the frames of mirrors or artworks. A large, indoor plant can add a touch of freshness to both rooms.\n\n**7. Shopping List:**\nMost items can be found at popular furniture stores like IKEA, Home Centre, and Pan Emirates. For more unique or industrial-style pieces, try visiting Al Quoz''s industrial area or Dragon Mart.\n\n**8. Timeline:**\nOnce all items have been sourced, the entire implementation - including painting, flooring installation, furniture setup, and final touches - can be completed within 3-4 weeks.\n\nFinally, considering Dubai''s hot climate, make sure to choose materials that do not absorb heat and make sure the space has adequate air conditioning. Given the cultural preferences, ensure the design provides enough privacy and space for hosting guests.\n\nPlease note that the above mentioned prices are approximate and may vary depending on the specific products chosen and the store of purchase.\n','\n',char(10)),'uguyguygyugyu','["bedroom","dining_room"]','["modern","industrial"]',2,'completed','[{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-Num5G8eQsRMqJwjykpEfskQt.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A32%3A28Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A32%3A28Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=cc612491-d948-4d2e-9821-2683df3719f5&sktid=a48cca56-e6da-484e-a814-9c849652bcb3&skt=2025-08-20T09%3A47%3A47Z&ske=2025-08-21T09%3A47%3A47Z&sks=b&skv=2024-08-04&sig=bY4SCiRVFp8vdL9qQAxNjkgZALv3EtGkgYfhxB%2BCbbI%3D","prompt":"Wide angle view, A beautiful modern and industrial bedroom, dining_room interior design in Dubai, UAE. High-quality architectural visualization with natural daylight. Clean, elegant space with attention to detail. Photorealistic rendering, interior design photography style. Luxurious finishes suitable for Dubai market. ","index":1},{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-zqoACQNUTIxg65gch4y2skaj.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A32%3A44Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A32%3A44Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&r