INSERT INTO design_image_generations VALUES(4,'ba3898c2-78df-4a54-9637-1f1c213b64cb',2,replace('**1. Color Scheme:**\nTo embrace the modern industrial style, opt for a neutral color palette with shades of grey, black, and white. Accent these with touches of warm tones like copper or brass. Here are some specific colors:\n\n- Resene Black White (#EDECE6): For the walls, to keep the space bright and open.\n- Dulux Timeless Grey (#D7D8DA): For the ceilings, providing a slight contrast with the walls.\n- Benjamin Moore Iron Mountain (#54524D): For the trim and architectural details. It''s a deep grey almost black that will give a modern and sharp look.\n- Dulux Copper Blush (#BB857A): As an accent color, could be used for cushions, throws, or decor pieces. It adds warmth and contrast to the space.\n\n**2. Layout Suggestions:**\nFor the bedroom, consider a king-size bed against the main wall, flanked by two industrial bedside tables. A slim console table opposite the bed can house a flat-screen TV. A small reading nook by the window could include an armchair and floor lamp. \n\nIn the dining room, a rectangular dining table with bench seating on one side and chairs on the other would work well. A sideboard against one wall can offer storage and a space for food serving. \n\n**3. Material Recommendations:**\nFlooring: Polished concrete flooring would be perfect for the industrial vibe. For a more comfortable touch, add area rugs in the bedroom and under the dining table.\n\nWall Finishes: Exposed brick walls would add to the industrial look. If not achievable, wallpapers that mimic this effect are available.\n\n**4. Furniture List:**\n- King-size industrial bed frame (2000 AED)\n- Pair of bedside tables (1000 AED)\n- Slim console table (750 AED)\n- Armchair (1000 AED)\n- Rectangular dining table (1500 AED)\n- Dining chairs and bench (1500 AED)\n- Sideboard (1000 AED)\n\n**5. Lighting Plan:**\n- Pendant lights with Edison bulbs over the bedside tables and dining table for ambient lighting (500 AED each)\n- Recessed ceiling lights for general lighting (2000 AED)\n- Floor lamp for the reading nook (500 AED)\n\n**6. Decor Elements:**\n- Framed vintage maps or industrial patents as artwork (500 AED each)\n- Copper or brass decorative pieces (500 AED)\n- Faux plants for a touch of greenery (500 AED)\n\n**7. Shopping List:**\nMost items can be found in IKEA, Home Centre, and Pan Emirates. You can also explore local markets for unique decor pieces.\n\n**8. Timeline:**\nThis project can be completed in 4-6 weeks. The first two weeks will be for purchasing and delivering furniture. The third week will be for installing lighting and setting up the furniture. The final week(s) will be for adding decor elements and final touches.\n\nRemember, these are just estimates and actual costs and timelines may vary. Always consider your personal preferences and the functionality of the space.','\n',char(10)),'uguyguygyugyu','["bedroom","dining_room"]','["modern","industrial"]',2,'completed','[{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-BQk2gm55g577pPRDqV4HENuV.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A33%3A01Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A33%3A01Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=77e5a8ec-6bd1-4477-8afc-16703a64f029&sktid=a48cca56-e6da-484e-a814-9c849652bcb3&skt=2025-08-20T13%3A53%3A19Z&ske=2025-08-21T13%3A53%3A19Z&sks=b&skv=2024-08-04&sig=skGwTGky4Lnpyps2W6i1gjOVtj%2BmSxDu4zo3nzL4SDw%3D","prompt":"Wide angle view, A beautiful modern and industrial bedroom, dining_room interior design in Dubai, UAE. High-quality architectural visualization with natural daylight. Clean, elegant space with attention to detail. Photorealistic rendering, interior design photography style. Luxurious finishes suitable for Dubai market. ","index":1},{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-QPSlecCCp5