INSERT INTO design_image_generations VALUES(5,'adb1d97c-8eae-445f-8ff0-14c603100d98',2,replace('**1. Color Scheme:** \n\nFor a modern bedroom with white walls in Dubai, we suggest a neutral color palette. \n\n- White: Hex #FFFFFF\n- Light Grey: Hex #D3D3D3\n- Dark Grey: Hex #A9A9A9\n- Beige: Hex #F5F5DC\n- Accents of Gold: Hex #FFD700\n\nThe white walls will help to keep the room feeling fresh and bright, while accents of gold will add a touch of luxury typical in Dubai''s design aesthetic. \n\n**2. Layout Suggestions:**\n\nThe layout should be minimalist and functional. Keep the bed as the central focus, flanked by two bedside tables. Consider a bench at the foot of the bed for added functionality. Use a large area rug under the bed to anchor the space. If space allows, add a reading corner with a comfortable chair and floor lamp.\n\n**3. Material Recommendations:**\n\n- Flooring: Opt for marble flooring, which is widely available and popular in Dubai for its cooling properties and luxe appeal. \n- Wall finishes: Keep the walls in a matte white finish for a crisp, modern look. Consider a feature wall with textured wallpaper or a mural behind the bed.\n- Window treatments: Use sheer white curtains for privacy while allowing natural light and blackout drapes for nighttime.\n\n**4. Furniture List:**\n\n- King-size Bed: AED 2,000\n- Bedside Tables x2: AED 1,000\n- Bench: AED 800\n- Reading Chair: AED 1,000\n- Floor Lamp: AED 400\n\n**5. Lighting Plan:**\n\nUse a mix of ambient, task, and accent lighting. Install a statement chandelier or pendant light over the bed. Use table lamps on bedside tables for reading and task lighting. Consider recessed lighting in the ceiling for a modern look and indirect lighting behind the bed for a cozy feel.\n\n**6. Decor Elements:**\n\n- Artwork: Choose abstract pieces in the room''s color scheme. \n- Plants: Opt for hardy indoor palms which thrive in Dubai''s climate.\n- Accessories: Use gold accents like picture frames, vases, and decorative bowls.\n- Rugs: A plush cream or beige area rug.\n\n**7. Shopping List:**\n\n- Furniture: IKEA, Marina Home, Home Centre\n- Lighting: ACE, Pan Emirates\n- Decor Elements: Crate&Barrel, The Bowery Company, Zara Home\n\n**8. Timeline:**\n\nAssuming all items are readily available, the project should take around 3-4 weeks. This includes time for shopping, delivery, assembly, and final styling touches. This is an estimate and actual timeline may vary based on availability and delivery times.\n\nRemember: It’s essential to incorporate personal style and preferences to make the space feel unique and truly yours.','\n',char(10)),'Modern bedroom with white walls','[]','[]',3,'completed','[{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-HMU6OoOa3jqWNmUNovsE5tVk.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A34%3A04Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A34%3A04Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=b1a0ae1f-618f-4548-84fd-8b16cacd5485&sktid=a48cca56-e6da-484e-a814-9c849652bcb3&skt=2025-08-20T16%3A34%3A04Z&ske=2025-08-21T16%3A34%3A04Z&sks=b&skv=2024-08-04&sig=SMrLyhIVGn1GYrYP8kn6rPoZumNVHvsYgFwYZalHpXw%3D","prompt":"Wide angle view, A beautiful modern interior space interior design in Dubai, UAE. High-quality architectural visualization with natural daylight. Clean, elegant space with attention to detail. Photorealistic rendering, interior design photography style. Luxurious finishes suitable for Dubai market. Incorporating elements: Modern bedroom with white walls","index":1},{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-YHla3JkJdifG8fVRLqcBjupD.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A34%3A25Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A34%3A25Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=ed3ea2f9-5e38-44be-9a1b-7c1e65e4d54f&sktid=a48cca56-e6da-484e-a814-9c849652bcb3&skt=2025-08-20T15%3A16%3A44Z&ske=2025-08-21T15%3A16%3A44Z&sks=b&skv=2024-08-