INSERT INTO design_image_generations VALUES(6,'fabd7e66-3fa7-40f0-bcfa-a0ee2b44a51c',2,replace('**1. Color Scheme:** \n\nThe color palette will be mainly neutral with shades of white, beige, and grey. A touch of blue and gold will be added for a hint of luxury. \n\n- Primary: White (#FFFFFF)\n- Secondary: Light Beige (#F5F5DC)\n- Accent 1: Grey (#808080)\n- Accent 2: Navy Blue (#000080)\n- Accent 3: Gold (#FFD700)\n\n**2. Layout Suggestions:**\n\nThe room should be divided into two sections - a formal seating area and an informal lounge area. The formal seating area should have a three-seater sofa and two accent chairs, a coffee table in the center, and a console table against the wall. The lounge area should have a large L-shaped couch. \n\n**3. Material Recommendations:**\n\n- Flooring: Light oak wooden flooring for a warm yet modern look. \n- Wall Finishes: Off-white paint for walls, with an accent wall in navy blue. \n\n**4. Furniture List:**\n\n- Formal Seating Area:\n  - Three-Seater Sofa (AED 2,000) \n  - Two Accent Chairs (AED 1,000 each) \n  - Coffee Table (AED 800) \n  - Console Table (AED 1,200) \n- Informal Lounge Area:\n  - L-Shaped Couch (AED 3,000)\n\n**5. Lighting Plan:**\n\n- Recessed Ceiling Lights: To provide overall illumination (AED 800)\n- Table Lamps: On the console table for focused lighting (AED 500)\n- Floor Lamp: Near the L-shaped couch for reading (AED 600)\n\n**6. Decor Elements:**\n\n- Cushions: Mix of white, beige, and navy blue (AED 300)\n- Rugs: A large beige rug for the formal seating area and a grey one for the lounge (AED 1,000)\n- Artwork: Abstract paintings in gold frames (AED 1,500)\n- Plants: Potted indoor plants like the Areca Palm or Money Plant (AED 500)\n\n**7. Shopping List:**\n\n- Furniture: IKEA, Home Centre\n- Lighting: ACE, IKEA\n- Decor: Crate & Barrel, Pottery Barn\n- Plants: Dubai Garden Centre\n\n**8. Timeline:**\n\n- Week 1-2: Purchase and delivery of furniture\n- Week 3: Installation of lighting fixtures\n- Week 4: Setup of decor and plants\n\nRemember to consider the local climate and culture when choosing materials and decor. For instance, the use of indoor plants not only adds a refreshing touch but also helps to purify the air in Dubai''s hot climate. Similarly, the color scheme and decor elements are inspired by the city''s coastal vibes and modern aesthetic.','\n',char(10)),'Simple modern living room','[]','[]',3,'completed','[{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-aKZHlnLOjqVjXENTatleOaIE.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A33%3A55Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A33%3A55Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=cc612491-d948-4d2e-9821-2683df3719f5&sktid=a48cca56-e6da-484e-a814-9c849652bcb3&skt=2025-08-19T20%3A00%3A23Z&ske=2025-08-20T20%3A00%3A23Z&sks=b&skv=2024-08-04&sig=kBSes87R\/P5%2Bw5LIj9mSDAidxV7%2BU29\/hfxtL7o6IXM%3D","prompt":"Wide angle view, A beautiful modern interior space interior design in Dubai, UAE. High-quality architectural visualization with natural daylight. Clean, elegant space with attention to detail. Photorealistic rendering, interior design photography style. Luxurious finishes suitable for Dubai market. Incorporating elements: Simple modern living room","index":1},{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-p0WHVPqyj7gE2ipEnIieQOeQ.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A34%3A06Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A34%3A06Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=f1dafa11-a0c2-4092-91d4-10981fbda051&sktid=a48cca56-e6da-484e-a814-9c849652bcb3&skt=2025-08-20T00%3A45%3A46Z&ske=2025-08-21T00%3A45%3A46Z&sks=b&skv=2024-08-04&sig=xEtadDp6GDKxekyoNN2EjYLRCnqtoI\/pHoYjnBn7DPs%3D","prompt":"Close-up detail shot, A beautiful modern interior space interior design in Dubai, UAE. High-quality architectural visualization with warm evening lighting. Clean, elegant space with attention to detail. 