INSERT INTO design_image_generations VALUES(7,'69dbf08e-450a-4578-947f-5967a7a15a66',2,replace('**Living Room**\n1. **Color Scheme**: Opt for a warm palette to create an inviting space. Use Benjamin Moore''s Navajo White (OC-95) for the walls, with accents of Moroccan Red (1309) and Caponata (AF-650) on trims and moldings. \n\n2. **Layout Suggestions**: Position the main sofa against the largest wall, with two armchairs on either side to form a cozy conversation area. Add a coffee table in the middle and a console table against the opposite wall. \n\n3. **Material Recommendations**: Choose marble flooring for its elegance and durability. Use fabric wallpaper in a subtle pattern for an added layer of texture. \n\n4. **Furniture List**: \n   - Main sofa: Chesterfield 3 Seater Sofa, AED 8000, Homes R Us\n   - Armchairs: Mason Armchair, AED 2000 each, Pan Emirates\n   - Coffee Table: Silas Coffee Table, AED 1500, Crate&Barrel\n   - Console Table: Brogan Console Table, AED 2500, Marina Home\n\n5. **Lighting Plan**: Install a crystal chandelier for ambient lighting, with table lamps on the console table for task lighting. \n\n6. **Decor Elements**: Add a Persian rug, gold-framed mirrors, and classic artworks. Include plush cushions and drapes in matching colors. \n\n7. **Shopping List**: \n   - Lighting: The One\n   - Wallpaper: Laura Ashley\n   - Artworks: Gallery One\n   - Mirrors and Accessories: Zara Home\n\n8. **Timeline**: Allow 2-3 months for sourcing, delivery, and installation. \n\n**Children''s Room**\n1. **Color Scheme**: Use Sherwin Williams'' Open Air (SW 6491) for walls, with accents of Meander Blue (SW 6484) and Energetic Orange (SW 6880) for a fun, youthful look.\n\n2. **Layout Suggestions**: Place the bed against the wall, with a desk on the opposite side for studying. A bookshelf and a wardrobe should be placed on the remaining walls. \n\n3. **Material Recommendations**: Use vinyl flooring for its ease of cleaning and durability. Choose washable paint for walls. \n\n4. **Furniture List**: \n   - Bed: Stuva/Fritids Loft Bed, AED 1500, Ikea\n   - Desk: Micke Desk, AED 300, Ikea\n   - Bookshelf: Billy Bookcase, AED 300, Ikea\n   - Wardrobe: Dombas Wardrobe, AED 500, Ikea\n\n5. **Lighting Plan**: Install a fun ceiling pendant for ambient lighting, with a desk lamp for task lighting. \n\n6. **Decor Elements**: Add colorful wall decals, a vibrant rug, and playful curtains. Include a bean bag for a cozy reading corner. \n\n7. **Shopping List**: \n   - Lighting: Ikea\n   - Wall Decals: Baby Shop\n   - Rug and Curtains: Pottery Barn Kids\n\n8. **Timeline**: Allow 1-2 months for sourcing, delivery, and installation. \n\nRemember to respect Dubai''s culture, especially in shared spaces. Avoid overtly sexual or religious artworks. As Dubai gets very hot, opt for light and airy fabrics, and ensure all rooms are well-ventilated. Always choose quality over quantity to ensure your spaces last.','\n',char(10)),'iosejfiosjdfo','["living_room","children_room"]','["classic"]',3,'completed','[{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-St5KLeNCUi4s96zDNoA360rv.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A36%3A38Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A36%3A38Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=f1dafa11-a0c2-4092-91d4-10981fbda051&sktid=a48cca56-e6da-484e-a814-9c849652bcb3&skt=2025-08-20T03%3A22%3A57Z&ske=2025-08-21T03%3A22%3A57Z&sks=b&skv=2024-08-04&sig=KeBpnBMBVxdaW9Yk4qJ1io34cqLW2pfvy4mhpYUGKs8%3D","prompt":"Wide angle view, A beautiful classic living_room, children_room interior design in Dubai, UAE. High-quality architectural visualization with natural daylight. Clean, elegant space with attention to detail. Photorealistic rendering, interior design photography style. Luxurious finishes suitable for Dubai market. ","index":1},{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-y