INSERT INTO design_image_generations VALUES(8,'e5e4a9f8-7e89-40e7-9b0c-3fead1b2f75c',2,replace('**1. Color Scheme:**\n\nThe color scheme for this kitchen will be a mix of warm neutrals and earth tones to create a cozy yet modern feel. \n\n- Primary Color: White Smoke (#F5F5F5)\n- Secondary Color: Taupe (#483C32)\n- Accent Color: Burnt Sienna (#E97451)\n\n**2. Layout Suggestions:**\n\nThe kitchen will be a U-shaped layout with an island in the center. This layout provides plenty of counter space and storage. The island will function as a breakfast bar with stools on one side. The stove and oven will be on one side of the U, the fridge on the opposite side, and the sink in the island.\n\n**3. Material Recommendations:**\n\n- Flooring: Consider using limestone tiles. They are durable, locally sourced, and fit the color scheme. \n- Wall finishes: Opt for a matte finish paint in the color White Smoke for the walls. Use a glossy subway tile in the color Taupe for the backsplash. \n- Countertops: Use a polished granite countertop in a color that complements the Taupe backsplash.\n\n**4. Furniture List:**\n\n- Kitchen Island with built-in sink: AED 8,000\n- Bar Stools (x3): AED 1,500 \n- Dining Set: AED 4,000\n- Built-in Oven: AED 3,000\n- Freestanding Fridge: AED 2,500\n\n**5. Lighting Plan:**\n\nIncorporate a mix of ambient, task, and accent lighting. Install recessed lighting in the ceiling for ambient light. Under-cabinet lights can provide task lighting. Pendant lights over the island will serve as both task and accent lighting.\n\n**6. Decor Elements:**\n\n- A large rug in Burnt Sienna under the dining set will add warmth and tie the color scheme together.\n- Hang a large mirror on one wall to create the illusion of more space.\n- Use green plants as decor elements to bring in some natural color and freshness. \n\n**7. Shopping List:**\n\n- Flooring: Al Hashem Marble, Dubai\n- Paint: Jotun Paints, Dubai\n- Kitchen Island and Cabinets: IKEA, Dubai\n- Bar Stools: Home Centre, Dubai\n- Dining Set: Pan Emirates, Dubai\n- Built-in Oven and Fridge: Sharaf DG, Dubai\n- Lighting: Light House, Dubai\n\n**8. Timeline:**\n\nThe estimated timeline to complete this project is 6-8 weeks. This includes time for ordering and delivering materials, installation, and final touches. \n\n- Weeks 1-2: Order and deliver materials\n- Weeks 3-4: Install flooring and paint walls\n- Weeks 5-6: Install cabinets, island, and appliances\n- Weeks 7-8: Install lighting, arrange furniture, and add decor elements.','\n',char(10)),'Cozy modern kitchen with island','[]','[]',3,'completed','[{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-AORUK2yjNLCWOJpj2V5egpIt.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A38%3A20Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A38%3A20Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=ed3ea2f9-5e38-44be-9a1b-7c1e65e4d54f&sktid=a48cca56-e6da-484e-a814-9c849652bcb3&skt=2025-08-20T09%3A43%3A07Z&ske=2025-08-21T09%3A43%3A07Z&sks=b&skv=2024-08-04&sig=oEbO5XZy2SW61yokqYt7NIHCD\/C%2B6GTmLgZmWclSMsw%3D","prompt":"Wide angle view, A beautiful modern interior space interior design in Dubai, UAE. High-quality architectural visualization with natural daylight. Clean, elegant space with attention to detail. Photorealistic rendering, interior design photography style. Luxurious finishes suitable for Dubai market. Incorporating elements: Cozy modern kitchen with island","index":1},{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-xW3mZAMH522wsJAJUkLT53OG.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A38%3A33Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A38%3A33Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=f1dafa11-a0c2-4092-91d4-10981fbda051&sktid=a48cca56-e6da-484e-a814-9c849652bcb3&skt=2025-08-20T16%3A21%3A17Z&ske=2025-08-21T16%3A21%3A17Z&sks=b&skv=2024-08-04&sig=zreqMZbSsw3s5lJYkcwXUkQCPONv\/fScPAw0FbcEvSY%3D","prompt":"Close-up detail shot, A beauti