INSERT INTO design_image_generations VALUES(11,'5e41c3a3-eea0-472a-8e44-e0fabe2200cc',2,replace('**1. Color Scheme:**\n\n- Main: Benjamin Moore - Kendall Charcoal (HC-166) - This dark grey will give an industrial touch to the space.\n- Accent: Farrow and Ball - Churlish Green (No.251) - This vibrant green will provide a classic contrast.\n- Neutral: Benjamin Moore - Chantilly Lace (OC-65) - This crisp white will help balance the strong main and accent colors.\n\n**2. Layout Suggestions:**\n\n- The bedroom should have a bed centrally placed with side tables on both sides. A wardrobe should be placed on the adjacent wall. \n- For the dining room, a dining table should be centered with chairs around it. A buffet table can be placed against one wall, with a mirror or artwork above it.\n\n**3. Material Recommendations:**\n\n- Flooring: Go for a polished concrete floor. It''s not only durable and easy to clean but also complements the industrial style.\n- Wall finishes: Exposed brick wall for one accent wall in each room to give the industrial feel. The rest of the walls can be painted in the chosen color scheme.\n\n**4. Furniture List:**\n\n- Bedroom: \n   - Industrial style metal bed: 2000 AED\n   - Wooden side tables: 500 AED each\n   - Classic style wooden wardrobe: 4000 AED\n- Dining Room: \n   - Classic wooden dining table: 3000 AED\n   - Industrial style metal chairs: 600 AED each\n   - Wooden Buffet table: 2000 AED\n\n**5. Lighting Plan:**\n\n- Bedroom: Install a classic chandelier in the center of the room with industrial style wall sconces on either side of the bed.\n- Dining Room: An industrial pendant light over the dining table will be perfect. Add a table lamp on the buffet table for extra light.\n\n**6. Decor Elements:**\n\n- Bedroom: Framed vintage maps, potted plants, and a classic style rug. \n- Dining Room: A large mirror or abstract artwork above the buffet table, a centerpiece for the dining table and a classic style rug.\n\n**7. Shopping List:**\n\nYou can find most items in popular furniture stores like IKEA, Home Centre, and Pan Emirates. For vintage or unique pieces, try local flea markets or online stores like Dubizzle.\n\n**8. Timeline:**\n\nAssuming all items are readily available, the entire project can be completed in 4-6 weeks. This includes shopping, painting, installation, and arranging decor.\n\nRemember that Dubai has a hot desert climate, so opt for lightweight and breathable fabrics for any upholstery. Also, the UAE culture appreciates a mix of modern and traditional, hence the blend of industrial and classic styles.','\n',char(10)),'Adijofoiajsfijfij','["bedroom","dining_room"]','["industrial","classic"]',3,'completed','[{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-FzaZ6AuGtyxT4vO4xRUDPWdT.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A46%3A35Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A46%3A35Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=8b33a531-2df9-46a3-bc02-d4b1430a422c&sktid=a48cca56-e6da-484e-a814-9c849652bcb3&skt=2025-08-20T16%3A07%3A59Z&ske=2025-08-21T16%3A07%3A59Z&sks=b&skv=2024-08-04&sig=3y4EpwlWL6BMbqfKv57T8jtUw%2BmwksmaFtohnpjNp6k%3D","prompt":"Wide angle view, A beautiful industrial and classic bedroom, dining_room interior design in Dubai, UAE. High-quality architectural visualization with natural daylight. Clean, elegant space with attention to detail. Photorealistic rendering, interior design photography style. Luxurious finishes suitable for Dubai market. ","index":1},{"url":"https:\/\/oaidalleapiprodscus.blob.core.windows.net\/private\/org-ilhWWDzx0WN6WdBJ9SUU5Xsl\/user-t1vqMPzgD9oUSWDBmz7H0TI0\/img-e37OFeZycx7f70QVUY0kLipM.png?st=2025-08-20T15%3A46%3A54Z&se=2025-08-20T17%3A46%3A54Z&sp=r&sv=2024-08-04&sr=b&rscd=inline&rsct=image\/png&skoid=cc612491-d948-4d2e-9821-2683df3719f5&sktid=a48cca56-e6da-484e-a814-9c849652bcb3&skt=2025-08-20T05%3A15%3A54Z&ske=2025-08-21T05%3A15%3A54Z&sks=b&skv=2024-08-04&sig=NoDjKjovcM8PfwLRNJotv9